# Resolve @fuzefront/* (e.g. @fuzefront/i18n) from GitHub Packages. Public deps
# still come from the default npm registry. The frontend Docker build context is
# only ./frontend, so this scoped config must live here (the repo-root .npmrc is
# not in the build context). CI/Docker provide GITHUB_TOKEN; for host dev the
# i18n runtime is resolved from local monorepo source via the Vite alias, so a
# token is not required locally.
@fuzefront:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${GITHUB_TOKEN}
